---
import Button from '@components/common/Button.astro';
---

<section class="overflow-hidden bg-bg-light py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Text (left on desktop) -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 gs-slide-left">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">WEDDING</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-[clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-primary">
          웨딩 포토부스
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          인생에서 가장 아름다운 날,<br />
          소중한 분들과의 순간을 더 특별하게.<br />
          우아한 디자인과 세심한 운영으로 완벽한 웨딩을 완성합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <Button href="/wedding" variant="primary" size="md">
            자세히 보기 →
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image (right on desktop) -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 gs-slide-right overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583939003579-730e3918a45a?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&q=90"
          alt="웨딩 포토부스"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
